123 the date thereof in the official organ of Clayton County. The ballot shall have written or
124 printed thereon the words:
125 "( ) YES Shall the Act be approved which provides a homestead exemption from
126 Clayton County ad valorem taxes for disabled veterans, senior citizens,
127 ( ) NO unremarried surviving spouses of a peace officer or firefighter killed in the
